columns.name: con_id
columns.description: container id

columns.name: workspace
columns.description: A work area mapped to one or more database schemas

columns.name: workspace_display_name
columns.description: Display name for the workspace

columns.name: column_name
columns.description: Name of column or synonym.  Used to match against columns when UI Defaults are used by create wizards.

columns.name: synonym_of
columns.description: If a synonym, the name of the base column that it is a synonym of.

columns.name: label
columns.description: Used for item label and report column heading.

columns.name: help_text
columns.description: Used for help text for items and interactive report columns.

columns.name: format_mask
columns.description: Used as the format mask for items and report columns.  Can be overwritten by report for form specific format masks.

columns.name: default_value
columns.description: Used as the default value for items.

columns.name: form_format_mask
columns.description: If provided, used as the format mask for items, overriding any value for the general format mask.

columns.name: form_display_width
columns.description: Used as the width of any items using this Attribute Definition.

columns.name: form_display_height
columns.description: Used as the height of any items using this Attribute Definition (only used by item types such as textares and shuttles).

columns.name: form_data_type
columns.description: Used as the data type for items (specifies whether this item contains VARCHAR or NUMBER data which results in an automatic validation).

columns.name: report_format_mask
columns.description: If provided, used as the format mask for report columns, overriding any value for the general format mask.

columns.name: report_col_alignment
columns.description: Used as the alignment for report column data (e.g. number are usually right justified).

columns.name: created_by
columns.description: User that created this column.

columns.name: created_on
columns.description: Date this column was created.

columns.name: last_updated_by
columns.description: APEX developer who made last update

columns.name: last_updated_on
columns.description: Date of last update
